# SCSS Conventions

- Pure SCSS with CSS custom properties — no Bootstrap, no Tailwind
- Mobile-first breakpoints: sm(480px), md(768px), lg(1024px), xl(1200px)
- Use `_variables.scss` tokens via CSS custom properties `var(--color-red)` etc.
- One partial per concern: `_header.scss`, `_hero.scss`, etc.
- `main.scss` imports all partials — this compiles to `assets/css/main.css`
- Max compiled CSS target: ~20-30kb
- Container max-width: 1200px
- Fonts: Boogaloo (display), Nunito (body) — enqueued in `inc/enqueue.php`
- Brand colors: see `wordpress-project.mdc` and `_variables.scss` (`--color-pink-light`, `--color-pink-dark`, etc.)
